&lt;p&gt;以上语录引自沈阳大街的传说虎哥，进一步了解如下:&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qY411x7uu?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&amp;amp;vd_source=080e8b4b2df6184dfbe8810414e19755&#34;  title=&#34;独立宣言&#34;
